  }
}
```

This sort of &quot;index&quot; makes it then easy to look up the chat rooms for a user.

I&#39;d also recommend reading my answer to:

* https://stackoverflow.com/questions/40656589/firebase-query-if-child-of-child-contains-a-value, of which this is essentially a variant
